('stores tag map in ctx.data')` - `ctx.data.set('taxonomy-tags', tagMap)`\n- `it('handles empty file list')` - Empty tag map\n- `it('tags are case-normalized to lowercase')` - 'JavaScript' and 'JAVASCRIPT' both become 'javascript'\n\n**Expected Plugin Behavior:**\n- Implements `beforeBuild` and `afterBuild` hooks\n- beforeBuild: Creates tag index map in `ctx.data['taxonomy-tags']`\n- afterBuild: Generates HTML pages at `tags/{tag}.html` listing all files with that tag\n- Normalizes tags to lowercase\n- Tag map: `Map<string, ContentFile[]>`\n\n---\n\n### 11. **tests/plugins/dev-server.test.ts** (Full Contents - 96 lines)\n\n**Dev Server Plugin Tests:**\n- `it('stores dev-server-config in ctx.data')` - Creates config object\n- `it('config includes port setting')` - Port number (default 3000)\n- `it('config includes asset routes from asset-pipeline')` - Reads `asset-manifest` from data\n- `it('config includes search index path')` - Sets `searchIndexPath: '/search-index.json'`\n- `it('config includes content routes')` - Routes for each HTML file with handler: 'static'\n- `it('default port is 3000')` - Port defaults to 3000\n- `it('handles missing asset-pipeline data gracefully')` - Empty assetPaths array if no manifest\n\n**Dev Server Config Structure:**\n```typescript\ninterface DevServerConfig {\n  port: number;\n  routes: Array<{ path: string; handler: string }>;\n  assetPaths: string[];\n  searchIndexPath: string;\n}\n```\n\n**Expected Plugin Behavior:**\n- Implements `afterBuild` hook\n- Creates config with port (3000), asset routes, content routes, and search index path\n- Reads `asset-manifest` from ctx.data if available\n- Generates routes for each HTML file in ctx.output\n\n---\n\n### 12. **tests/plugins/rss-feed.test.ts** (Full Contents - 121 lines)\n\n**RSS Feed Plugin Tests:**\n- `it('generates valid RSS 2.0 XML')` - Valid XML with `<?xml version=\"1.0\"`, `<rss version=\"2.0\">`, `<channel>`, `<item>`\n- `it('feed items contain HTML content not raw markdown